cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.MM 

This paper is about Congested Scene Recognition using deep learning methods, specifically convolutional neural networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). Additionally, the paper involves training the model using large datasets, which falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The use of deep learning also suggests cs.LG (Machine Learning) as a possible category. The paper also involves optimization of the model, which could fall under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper involves counting objects, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia).
